\name{paf-package}
\alias{paf-package}
\docType{package}
\title{
Income Polarization Index
}

\description{
Description: The PaF income polarization index as proposed by Duclos J. Y., Esteban, J. and Ray D. (2004). "Polarization: concepts, measurement, estimation". Econometrica, 72(6): 1737--1772. The index may be computed for a single or for a range of values of the \eqn{\alpha}-parameter. Bootstrapping is also available.
}

